1
00:00:08,541 --> 00:00:09,625
I'm Mai Taniyama,

2
00:00:09,708 --> 00:00:11,291
a freshman in high school

3
00:00:11,375 --> 00:00:12,500
and I work part-time

4
00:00:12,583 --> 00:00:15,750
with a team of professional
ghost hunters.

5
00:00:15,833 --> 00:00:17,166
It was one thing
when we found out

6
00:00:17,250 --> 00:00:20,250
that the doll Minnie was
behind the poltergeist,

7
00:00:20,333 --> 00:00:21,625
but everything changed

8
00:00:21,708 --> 00:00:24,583
once Minnie tried to physically
harm little Ayami.

9
00:00:26,250 --> 00:00:28,000
Naru did tons of research

10
00:00:28,083 --> 00:00:29,958
on the previous
owners of the house

11
00:00:30,041 --> 00:00:32,416
and found out that lots of
children around eight years old

12
00:00:32,500 --> 00:00:34,250
who have lived
here have died,

13
00:00:34,333 --> 00:00:36,500
one after the other.

14
00:00:36,583 --> 00:00:37,916
Going off the idea

15
00:00:38,000 --> 00:00:39,458
that the children's spirits
were trapped in the house

16
00:00:39,541 --> 00:00:41,541
and possessing Minnie,

17
00:00:41,625 --> 00:00:45,375
Naru called in John and
Masako as reinforcements.

18
00:00:45,458 --> 00:00:46,375
And then...

19
00:00:47,791 --> 00:00:49,416
Monk, I'd like you to try
cleansing the house again.

20
00:00:49,500 --> 00:00:52,041
But once Monk started
his exorcism,

21
00:00:52,125 --> 00:00:53,625
things took a turn
for the worst.

22
00:00:53,708 --> 00:00:55,666
Tomiko...

23
00:00:55,750 --> 00:00:57,000
Tomiko...

24
00:00:58,250 --> 00:00:59,625
my... child.

25
00:01:01,166 --> 00:01:03,750
What am I looking at?

26
00:01:03,833 --> 00:01:06,208
And who in the
world is Tomiko?

27
00:01:08,958 --> 00:01:14,958
[Music]

28
00:02:45,541 --> 00:02:48,875
Naumaku san manda
bazaradan sendamakaro

29
00:02:48,958 --> 00:02:52,958
shata sowataya un
tarata, kan man.

30
00:02:53,041 --> 00:02:54,750
Naumaku san manda
bodaran, on boron.

31
00:02:54,833 --> 00:02:56,125
Monk, there's
something behind you!

32
00:02:58,083 --> 00:02:59,833
What? There's nothing
in here Naru!

33
00:03:00,958 --> 00:03:02,583
Damn... I guess
he can't see it.

34
00:03:03,791 --> 00:03:04,833
Mai, wait!

35
00:03:11,500 --> 00:03:12,500
Monk... Look out!

36
00:03:12,583 --> 00:03:13,958
Go...! Right now!

37
00:03:16,208 --> 00:03:17,708
But...

38
00:03:17,791 --> 00:03:19,625
We can see the
ghost on camera.

39
00:03:19,708 --> 00:03:20,958
Don't just stand
there, Mai!

40
00:03:21,041 --> 00:03:22,416
Get out of here!

41
00:03:22,500 --> 00:03:23,875
Come quick!
You're in danger!

42
00:03:26,166 --> 00:03:28,375
No one can interfere with me.

43
00:03:33,750 --> 00:03:34,958
Mai!

44
00:03:35,041 --> 00:03:36,916
Naumaku san manda
bazaradan kan!!

45
00:03:40,875 --> 00:03:43,250
-Mai! Are you okay...?
-Yeah.

46
00:03:43,333 --> 00:03:44,750
Come on. Let's go.

47
00:03:56,916 --> 00:03:59,458
It looks like the house
was built over this well.

48
00:03:59,541 --> 00:04:01,625
It must be pretty old.

49
00:04:01,708 --> 00:04:04,375
There's the spirit
of an OSHIMA here

50
