children's spirits

52
00:04:08,875 --> 00:04:11,208
and pretending to
be their mother...

53
00:04:11,291 --> 00:04:14,125
The children only
want to return home,

54
00:04:14,208 --> 00:04:16,333
but they're lost and
can't find their way out.

55
00:04:17,583 --> 00:04:19,916
Is Minnie there too?

56
00:04:20,000 --> 00:04:23,208
Minnie, who is actually
Yuki Tachibana,

57
00:04:23,291 --> 00:04:25,708
acts as the ringleader
of the children,

58
00:04:25,791 --> 00:04:29,666
but in reality, she is in
so much pain and sadness

59
00:04:29,750 --> 00:04:31,791
that she just wants all
of this all to stop.

60
00:04:44,166 --> 00:04:47,583
It appears to me that this
well bores deep into the earth.

61
00:04:47,666 --> 00:04:49,916
And At the very bottom,

62
00:04:50,000 --> 00:04:53,458
lie the spirits of the children,
trapped in the dark.

63
00:04:53,541 --> 00:04:55,625
Who is this Tomiko?

64
00:04:55,708 --> 00:04:57,708
It's Oshima's child.

65
00:04:57,791 --> 00:04:59,791
She's looking
for her child.

66
00:04:59,875 --> 00:05:02,083
Tomiko is her daughter.

67
00:05:02,166 --> 00:05:05,208
That's why she's
gathering the children.

68
00:05:05,291 --> 00:05:06,708
Now we're getting somewhere.

69
00:05:09,208 --> 00:05:10,791
Naru?

70
00:05:10,875 --> 00:05:13,083
I need to take
care of something.

71
