Okay guys...

80
00:05:31,208 --> 00:05:33,166
-Who wants to go?
-Hmm?

81
00:05:33,250 --> 00:05:35,166
Which of you two is up
to the challenge...?

82
00:05:35,250 --> 00:05:37,500
I'm warning you it's
intense in there.

83
00:05:40,791 --> 00:05:42,416
Fine, I guess I'll do it...

84
