Ayami for me.

86
00:05:45,958 --> 00:05:46,916
-Of Course.
-Sure thing.

87
00:05:50,041 --> 00:05:52,208
May the heart of this
house be cleansed

88
00:05:52,291 --> 00:05:54,000
as thy interim dwelling,

89
00:05:54,083 --> 00:05:55,750
and enshrine thyself in
this altar of peace.

90
00:05:55,833 --> 00:05:57,416
