And of Emperor Yamato,

97
00:06:15,041 --> 00:06:17,416
who reigns over the Land of
the Eight Grand Islands...

98
00:06:28,958 --> 00:06:31,250
What did you stop for?

99
00:06:31,333 --> 00:06:32,500
Take it easy.

100
00:06:34,500 --> 00:06:35,750
What's wrong?

101
00:06:35,833 --> 00:06:37,583
I just felt
someone touch me!

102
00:06:37,666 --> 00:06:39,333
