103
00:06:39,416 --> 00:06:40,875
You're a professional, remember?

104
00:06:42,666 --> 00:06:43,791
Mai... What's wrong?

105
00:06:46,458 --> 00:06:47,916
I can feel a...

106
00:06:48,000 --> 00:06:49,041
hand on my...

107
00:06:50,250 --> 00:06:51,541
Help!

108
00:06:51,625 --> 00:06:53,125
Mai!

109
00:06:53,208 --> 00:06:54,416
