Stop!

122
00:08:07,666 --> 00:08:09,166
Tomiko!

123
00:08:09,250 --> 00:08:11,708
Tomiko! Tomiko!

124
00:08:11,791 --> 00:08:13,291
Is that the girl's mother?

125
00:08:13,375 --> 00:08:14,708
Tomiko!

126
00:08:19,791 --> 00:08:21,916
NOOOO!

127
00:08:37,291 --> 00:08:38,291
Don't...!

128
00:08:40,250 --> 00:08:41,208
Naru?

129
00:08:46,500 --> 00:08:47,708
Tomiko.

130
00:08:50,750 --> 00:08:52,000
Don't do it!

131
00:08:58,666 --> 00:09:00,500
Mai! Are you Hurt?

132
00:09:01,125 --> 00:09:02,750
Ayako.

133
00:09:02,833 --> 00:09:05,083
Oh, thank goodness
you're okay Mai, ...

134
00:09:05,166 --> 00:09:07,666
Just sit tight. Lin's coming
right down to help you.

135
00:09:07,750 --> 00:09:09,541
Oh yeah...
That's right...

136
00:09:09,625 --> 00:09:11,125
I was dragged down
into the well.

137
00:09:13,708 --> 00:09:15,833
Really...? A kidnapping?

138
00:09:15,916 --> 00:09:16,833
That's right...

139
00:09:16,916 --> 00:09:18,250
at 'least I think so.

140
00:09:18,333 --> 00:09:19,750
It was a vision...

141
00:09:19,833 --> 00:09:21,375
This man just strolls
up to the girl

142
00:09:21,458 --> 00:09:22,916
and then walks
away with her...

143
