176
00:10:50,083 --> 00:10:52,083
Aren't you two supposed
to be watching Ayami?

177
00:10:52,166 --> 00:10:54,416
She could be in danger
right now for all you know!

178
00:10:54,500 --> 00:10:56,583
Naru said there's no use
in guarding her anymore.

179
00:10:56,666 --> 00:10:58,041
So we came back to help.

180
00:10:58,125 --> 00:11:01,333
Wait... Are you positive
that she's okay?

181
00:11:01,416 --> 00:11:03,625
She's fine...

182
00:11:03,708 --> 00:11:05,500
Everything will
be over tonight.

183
00:11:14,666 --> 00:11:17,041
Miss Hara... Can you see
what the spirits are doing?

184
00:11:18,833 --> 00:11:20,333
They're in the
living room...

185
00:11:20,416 --> 00:11:23,333
There's no indication they've
gone to the hotel yet.

186
00:11:23,416 --> 00:11:24,875
Matsuzaki

187
00:11:24,958 --> 00:11:26,041
Start making charms

188
00:11:26,125 --> 00:11:28,333
that will stop any
spirits from passing.

189
00:11:28,416 --> 00:11:31,166
I want the rest of you to post
them throughout the house.

190
00:11:31,250 --> 00:11:33,625
We're going to raise a
kekkai barrier in here.

191
00:11:33,708 --> 00:11:35,875
Care to fill us
in on the plan?

192
00:11:35,958 --> 00:11:38,750
I'm planning on returning
Tomiko back to her mother.

193
00:11:38,833 --> 00:11:39,833
Huh?

194
00:11:39,916 --> 00:11:41,791
That's impossible, Naru.

195
00:11:41,875 --> 00:11:44,125
Tomiko cannot be
returned physically.

196
00:11:44,208 --> 00:11:46,333
Her mother will continue
to haunt this place

197
00:11:46,416 --> 00:11:48,875
until we can at least create
the illusion of her return.

198
00:11:48,958 --> 00:11:51,250
So we'll need substitute.

199
00:11:52,916 --> 00:11:54,541
You don't mean
Ayami, do you?

200
00:11:58,833 --> 00:12:00,541
The problem lies
with the woman...

201
00:12:00,625 --> 00:12:02,583
If we leave here
without removing her,

202
00:12:02,666 --> 00:12:03,791
we'll have failed.

203
00:12:03,875 --> 00:12:05,791
But this woman
is dangerous...

204
00:12:05,875 --> 00:12:07,458
She nearly killed
Mai an hour ago

205
00:12:07,541 --> 00:12:09,083
when she pulled her
into the well...

206
00:12:09,166 --> 00:12:10,291
I think at some point

207
00:12:10,375 --> 00:12:12,666
we need to start
considering our own safety.

208
00:12:12,750 --> 00:12:13,750
I guess...

209
00:12:13,833 --> 00:12:15,291
but what about Ayami?

210
00:12:25,083 --> 00:12:26,291
Come on guys.

211
00:12:29,541 --> 00:12:31,583
I must say I'm disappointed
in all of you...

212
00:12:31,666 --> 00:12:33,541
I expected much more.

213
00:12:33,625 --> 00:12:35,416
If you can't even
think objectively,

214
00:12:35,500 --> 00:12:36,666
then I don't need you.

215
00:12:36,750 --> 00:12:37,750
But the risks are high.

216
00:12:37,833 --> 00:12:39,166
If we screw this up

217
00:12:39,250 --> 00:12:40,791
our spirits could be
trapped here as well.

218
00:12:47,041 --> 00:12:48,791
Whether or not you
want to participate

219
00:12:48,875 --> 00:12:50,916
is entirely up to you.

220
00:12:51,000 --> 00:12:53,416
Mai, You're free
to leave as well.

221
00:12:53,500 --> 00:12:54,833
Naru.

222
00:13:02,291 --> 00:13:03,750
You poor thing, Mai...

223
00:13:03,833 --> 00:13:06,916
He's quite a handful.

224
00:13:07,000 --> 00:13:08,833
If Naru is prepared
to go that far

225
00:13:08,916 --> 00:13:11,291
then there's at least
a chance of success.

226
00:13:11,375 --> 00:13:14,208
Why is she so pro-Naru
all of a sudden?

227
00:13:14,291 --> 00:13:15,916
I trust your judgment Masako

228
00:13:16,000 --> 00:13:17,791
and if you think we
should then let's do it.

229
00:13:17,875 --> 00:13:19,500
You sure?

230
00:13:19,583 --> 00:13:22,041
Well at this point it's
the only option we have.

231
00:13:22,125 --> 00:13:23,833
I agree. I think
it's a good plan.

232
00:13:26,208 --> 00:13:29,541
If you all end up dead
I'll see to your funeral.

233
00:13:29,625 --> 00:13:30,833
Well, how nice.

234
00:13:32,458 --> 00:13:33,916
Just like Naru told us,

235
00:13:34,000 --> 00:13:36,500
we began putting up charms
all throughout the house.

236
00:13:45,500 --> 00:13:47,208
So... what exactly

237
00:13:47,291 --> 00:13:49,416
is the purpose of putting
these charms everywhere?

238
00:13:49,500 --> 00:13:50,666
It's simple...

239
00:13:50,750 --> 00:13:53,208
To keep the spirits
from leaving the house.

240
00:13:53,291 --> 00:13:54,625
Naru!

241
00:13:54,708 --> 00:13:56,666
Be aware that we'll be
leaving the demongate open

242
00:13:56,750 --> 00:13:58,541
to distribute the spirits.

243
00:13:59,500 --> 00:14:01,041
Oh get off it...

244
00:14:01,125 --> 00:14:03,000
Why does he have to
act like a bigshot?

245
00:14:03,083 --> 00:14:05,458
'Cause he's Naru.

246
00:14:05,541 --> 00:14:08,333
Uhh, did he say
Demon's Gate?

247
00:14:08,416 --> 00:14:09,750
No Demongate...

248
00:14:09,833 --> 00:14:11,500
The northeast quarter...

249
00:14:11,583 --> 00:14:14,250
It's the easiest direction
for spirits to pass through.

250
00:14:14,333 --> 00:14:16,791
Monk and Matsuzaki
guard the demongate...

251
00:14:16,875 --> 00:14:18,333
And When the
spirits exit...

252
00:14:18,416 --> 00:14:20,958
scatter them as
best you can.

253
00:14:21,041 --> 00:14:23,500
So we'll be reducing the number
of spirits temporarily

254
00:14:23,583 --> 00:14:25,125
to draw the woman out?

255
00:14:25,208 --> 00:14:27,083
John I want you to
cover the living room

256
00:14:27,166 --> 00:14:28,166
and do the same.

257
00:14:28,250 --> 00:14:29,333
Piece of cake!

258
00:14:29,416 --> 00:14:30,625
Wait, hold on a second.

259
00:14:30,708 --> 00:14:33,458
Then Who's going to
conduct the exorcism?

260
00:14:33,541 --> 00:14:34,625
You don't mean...

261
00:15:01,500 --> 00:15:03,666
Our father,
who art in heaven.

262
00:15:04,666 --> 00:15:08,500
Hallowed be thy name.

263
00:15:08,583 --> 00:15:09,833
What's wrong?

264
00:15:09,916 --> 00:15:12,000
Cleansings are addressed
to the spirit directly

265
00:15:12,083 --> 00:15:15,375
to help them with issues they
had in their past lives...

266
00:15:15,458 --> 00:15:17,875
Only a medium can
be successful at it.

267
00:15:20,083 --> 00:15:21,916
Naru is no medium,

